WEBVTT

00:08:59.259 --> 00:09:00.601
Imagine this:

00:09:01.347 --> 00:09:03.006
you're a woman,

00:09:03.030 --> 00:09:04.443
you're married,

00:09:04.467 --> 00:09:05.621
you have a kid.

00:09:06.834 --> 00:09:08.618
You post something on social media,

00:09:08.642 --> 00:09:11.528
and in a reply,
you're told that you'll be raped,

00:09:12.577 --> 00:09:14.137
that your son will be watching,

00:09:14.825 --> 00:09:16.681
details of when and where.

00:09:17.148 --> 00:09:20.291
In fact, your home address
is put online for everyone to see.

00:09:21.580 --> 00:09:23.587
That feels like a pretty real threat.

00:09:25.113 --> 00:09:26.769
Do you think you'd go home?

00:09:27.999 --> 00:09:31.047
Do you think you'd continue doing
the thing that you were doing?